subject: United States Open (Tennis)
Tennis
lead_paragraph: Rafael Nadal showed the poise of what Patrick McEnroe called “a clear-cut favorite” before the tournament and dismissed the qualifier Ryler DeHeart, 6-1, 6-2, 6-4.
